main event: A civilian reported observing two unidentified flying objects in Collierville, Tennessee, on the nights of November 1 and 2, 1966.
interesting points: The objects were observed for a total duration of 15 minutes,The observer reported seeing a permanent brilliant white color with blinking lights at intervals,There were other family members present who witnessed the objects,The observer estimated the objects' distance as 1-1.5 miles away,The objects appeared to have varied courses during the observation.
witness description: A civilian male aged 20-24 with family
